The,service,provides,access,to,a,number,of,datasets,containing,recorded,levels,of,environmental,variables,measured,and,tracked,by,the,U,S,Environmental,Protection,Agency,A,number,of,datasets,document,various,monitoring,programs,over,time,tracking,pollutants,and,environmental,conditions,affecting,air,quality,water,quality,and,land,borne,contaminants,EPA,staff,and,contractors,can,access,both,current,and,historical,data,via,the,service,built,as,an,instance,of,ESRI,Geoportal,Server,API,methods,support,listing,of,available,datasets,and,selection,of,desired,data,based,on,location,and,conditions,of,interest,to,a,researcher,Methods,also,support,retrieval,of,desired,datasets,in,formats,suitable,for,further,analysis